data.description: Looking to live close to the beach and not pay beach prices? Here it is! This 2-bedroom 2 full bath home is available in Coral Ridge Subdivision just 3 miles to Carolina Beach. These homes don't come along very often so don't miss your opportunity to be part of this community.   This charming home is on a corner lot on a cul-de-sac and pond frontage.  Offering hardwood floors in living room, dining room and kitchen.  One bedroom and full bath downstairs and one bedroom and full bath upstairs which is perfect for a roommate situation.  Skylights in living room and plenty of other windows to bring in alot of natural light.  During the summer you can enjoy the community saltwater pool just across the street while the HOA takes care of the landscaping. Very low maintenance investment.  Newer HVAC 2021. No rentals less than 12 months.
